title: Exclusive: GE nears deal to sell over $30 billion of loans to Wells Fargo - source
text:
Published By: Reuters - Business - Today 
(Reuters) - General Electric Co is in advanced talks to sell a specialty finance portfolio, worth more than $30 billion, to Wells Fargo & Co...
